[center][img]http://jpegshare.net/images/fa/a5/faa5c2e5b6bb306c66e8dc116846d831.png[/img][/center]
Plugin replace the men\'s underwear. Plugin based on the model from \"Just for Fun CM PUNK by NEO\" and textures from \"Improved NPC Clothing - High Res\".

[center][img]http://jpegshare.net/images/c8/32/c8321d2340067961055811b093ee786a.png[/img][/center]
Plugin is compatible with any body retextures. Partially compatible with FavoredSoul replacer.

[center][img]http://jpegshare.net/images/f1/dc/f1dc8a90645c4ea7e49be7c2ee8b8c2a.png[/img][/center]
Neovinci for \"Just for Fun CM PUNK by NEO\": http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18804
BaronDavid for \"Improved NPC Clothing - High Res\": http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2674
